snippet.title: Froggy's Farm & Friends | ON Steam Game
snippet.description:
Help a friendly frog named Phroge as they farm, craft, and explore. Plant and grow crops for potion crafting, discover their unique magical qualities, and explore to uncover new friends! 

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2073410/Froggys_Farm__Friends/
